{"tid":673683,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"(石塘咀)而家根本成唔到間沾麵舖","createTime":"2018-05-22T05:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T10:57:37.000Z","uid":153946,"like":19,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a1144c86f2fd5deccbfe1c3059f653b296afd567","tid":673683,"uid":153946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T05:08:21.000Z","msg":"由pub咗之後 次次行過都見到條人龍勁長<br />\n間唔中溫完書趕完deadline 想落去畀自己食吓好少少嘅野，呢個sem係幾乎唔洗諗食彩<br />\n<br />\n但矛盾嘅係 真心支持佢嘅人客 (例如可能係吸滿幾次印嘅你同我) 都會想佢好生意<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =可唔可以變返隱世 真係次次行過想食都食唔到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 間野咁好生意 以後食唔到都ok 為佢開心"},{"pid":"a1aca80eb01eb4fd282d259df0d63f8445a61952","tid":673683,"uid":2153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T05:09:11.000Z","msg":"邊間？"},{"pid":"67a212beb6f8fd1c6c68a24a97b40c7d4f20adc1","tid":673683,"uid":153946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T05:14:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊間？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n後巷"},{"pid":"bccde5fa4ce86989856c60590f386a9d4a691bab","tid":673683,"uid":153946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T05:14:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊間？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n後巷</blockquote><br />\n後巷<span style=\"color: red;\">嗰間</span>"},{"pid":"f67282e45b10cee5ebc7d8a6bec19c972cbaf0b7","tid":673683,"uid":77717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"彩？"},{"pid":"12b6f76adef9da29714f2ebdfeefae26d4f894a1","tid":673683,"uid":153946,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T05:17:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>彩？</blockquote><br />\n內文唔係有講咩，係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89bdb2f1dd1c0adfde912413ff8cbc17c01fb91d","tid":673683,"uid":18666,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T05:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass